{"tid":2129890,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府強調一直聽從專家意見 政府與專家不存在意見分歧","createTime":"2020-07-29T02:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T11:52:08.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c94b11bc630190af3b42da4891704282ffdb1520","tid":2129890,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:26:23.000Z","msg":"政府晚上重申, 豁免檢疫安排實際上有必要, 以維持必須的社會及經濟運作, 並確保市民生活所需不受影響, 包括從陸路, 航運及空運輸入食品、日用品及其他貨物等.<br />\n        發言人說, 政府在本月19日發出題為「政府澄清豁免強制檢疫安排屬必要」的新聞稿, 是基於當時有評論指, 豁免強制檢疫安排帶來檢疫漏洞, 建議全面取消豁免機制. 因此, 政府需要針對性地就豁免機制對本港運作的必要性作出澄清, 以釋除這方面的誤解. 政府絕非否定專家就疫情源頭所提出的專業見解, 但有關澄清被解讀為政府與專家持不同意見. 事實上, 政府在防疫抗疫工作上, 一直尊重專家意見, 未來政府亦會繼續與專家保持密切溝通, 並與各本地學術團隊合作研究, 為防疫抗疫工作提供更多實證基礎."},{"pid":"171003c1d68b2c2aaecdaa9224a61f951330bf57","tid":2129890,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"ed0239ee263fa07afae065dacbeb9e7a6ea7e1e5","tid":2129890,"uid":42202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"成篇都無講政府與專家不存在意見分歧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a611023711eaa7a62795485ad16c826430d578","tid":2129890,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"冇即係有<br />\n用呢個態度睇popo同港共啲野包冇錯"},{"pid":"9b7ac79d48aed75a0727f644b40dd0f148f1e879","tid":2129890,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:28:15.000Z","msg":"尊重專家，但更專重國家（個黨）"},{"pid":"e01cbeab3acbfc0587d504740039dda2a6407fca","tid":2129890,"uid":50196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:29:05.000Z","msg":"意見接受<br />\n態度照舊"},{"pid":"02268b686aaea6086019b2ac9d456a21d136b5ab","tid":2129890,"uid":113000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"尋日有線訪門<br />\n<br />\n專家小組講明高峰期一次都冇搵佢地<br />\n<br />\n專家只係到等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又吹水"},{"pid":"86b90cfda58f42baca0e2c41235d8c0fcfb76e84","tid":2129890,"uid":55854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:29:53.000Z","msg":"平衡時空"},{"pid":"397efc23e9f89af1a6237e6025cdaf45d09388f5","tid":2129890,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:29:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abaa00f249f13f511e82c67e741cb7a560e632f5","tid":2129890,"uid":44935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:30:18.000Z","msg":"每日笑話"},{"pid":"fafafb405cce1fe2b52fc47df26c7bdc926d460f","tid":2129890,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:32:28.000Z","msg":"睇得出袁國勇發脾氣先咁勇串中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38650466db9eceee788d714a0da4e9c672e3cf96","tid":2129890,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:35:08.000Z","msg":"尊重專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尊重國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf02e6cd8d7bb6d1edb642befafac9c430a8b61e","tid":2129890,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:35:38.000Z","msg":"無分歧 只係加入左政治考慮 所以出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/29/103454_cf2d41aea1619bd298296152bf534713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F29%2F103454_cf2d41aea1619bd298296152bf534713.jpg&h=7a22bc40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"715a58d1b85752e039bb80838b04ac759439a2f2","tid":2129890,"uid":136716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一言堂 梗係冇"},{"pid":"72c6a526122163b757ff6c7f85db75022cc91c60","tid":2129890,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"每天看着確診數字上升，專家組成員福田敬二都說這次比上兩波更難應付，他與另外三位專家組成員一樣，認為引發這一波是政府豁免海員，機組人員檢疫。他說相信政府有認真聽專家意見，但做決定時可能有其他考慮。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">據了解，上一次開會是7月初，即疫情最嚴峻的這兩個多星期沒有再開專家組會議。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-cn.facebook.com/icablenews/posts/1514102325448497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-cn.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fposts%2F1514102325448497&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=5d32945d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-cn.facebook.com/icablenews/posts/1514102325448497</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1157827fc85cdad1aad2e88df8e42c593545afa","tid":2129890,"uid":298523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"意見無分歧<br />\n行政黨話事"},{"pid":"4da49983c2d3a47a0d05bf53f113c882f663c085","tid":2129890,"uid":121259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:41:08.000Z","msg":"聽專家意見，不過冇跟住做啫"},{"pid":"7c89359a1fb139d93857be0d5dde030658868f02","tid":2129890,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"政府專家顧問港大公共衛生學院院長福田敬二<br />\n及中大醫學院呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌向眾新聞表示，<br />\n並無參與是否押後立法會選舉的討論。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌也說，專家顧問團並無沒有牽涉押後立法會選舉的討論，<br />\n強調純粹是政府內部決定，「唔關我哋事」<br />\n<br />\n咁係咩專家認為推遲一年選舉有助抗疫？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/333Uvsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F333Uvsc&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=e5ea0954\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/333Uvsc</a>"},{"pid":"3aab15204b7d84e60769272e2981329a3cc8bc70","tid":2129890,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:44:11.000Z","msg":"無錯呀，佢係有聽架<br />\n不過聽完就算，政治行先，老人家條命排後<br />\n實係嬲區選D老人家唔落力排隊投票，攪到親共派慘敗，好陰毒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6790698fd8253035f148798c92580aa0827ad0","tid":2129890,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:45:30.000Z","msg":"尊重專家意見<br />\n舊年都話尊重市民意見，結果呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66519c0159108149978de4ccdda77a3cfa2039ae","tid":2129890,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:48:30.000Z","msg":"有聽, 不過唔接受"},{"pid":"e3eac6ef9e1cca8cd297dce64fa884418bbdfd10","tid":2129890,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"想屈專家教政府咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddae811a3faa32d9bf6c55aee33920508cc34a1","tid":2129890,"uid":265662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"一意孤行點可能有分歧？"},{"pid":"72eb8b832dc6952230127ea039a34591a1299d6b","tid":2129890,"uid":175428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02268b686aaea6086019b2ac9d456a21d136b5ab","tid":2129890,"uid":113000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"尋日有線訪門<br />\n<br />\n專家小組講明高峰期一次都冇搵佢地<br />\n<br />\n專家只係到等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又吹水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:52:08.000Z","msg":"對上一次係7月11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}